A Data-Centric Introduction to Computing — Jayret Edition

This work is a modified version of "A Data-Centric Introduction to Computing",
originally by Kathi Fisler, Shriram Krishnamurthi, Benjamin S. Lerner, and
Joe Gibbs Politz at Brown University.

